sentences: This item ( FCCC/SBI/2007/INF.1 and INF.5 ) was introduced in SBI plenary on Monday, 7 May.
Chair Asadi noted that he would consult informally with parties and draft conclusions, which were adopted on 18 May.
enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
